Auto-Scroll Behavior:
- Initial delay: 1s after page load
- Interval: 4s per slide
- Animation: translateX with 500ms ease-in-out transition
- Loop: After last image, smoothly reset to first (or duplicate set for seamless loop)

Pause on Hover:
- Mouse enter: clearInterval(autoScroll)
- Mouse leave: resume after 1s delay

Touch Gestures (Mobile):
- Swipe left/right: navigate prev/next
- Swipe velocity >0.5: skip to next slide
- Snap to item center after release

Accessibility:
- Role: region, aria-label="Project image carousel"
- ARIA live region: Announce "Slide X of Y" on change (polite)
- Keyboard: Arrow keys navigate, Tab skips carousel (not focusable images)

Reduced Motion:
- prefers-reduced-motion: No auto-scroll, show manual prev/next buttons
